"what_is_margin_ans" : "保证金交易是一种使用第三方借入的资金（即杠杆）进行交易的方法。保证金交易使交易者可以获得比自己拥有的更多的资本，因此，他们可以利用增加的资本获得更高的回报。另一方面，这也意味着交易者的损失可能远远超过其自有资金，因此应谨慎进行保证金交易。"

"what_is_leverage_ans" : "El apalancamiento se refiere al mayor poder de negociación que está disponible en el trading con margen. El apalancamiento te permite hacer que las posiciones de compra o venta sean más grandes que la cantidad de dinero en tu cuenta de trading. El apalancamiento se expresa como una relación entre la cantidad de dinero que tienes y la cantidad de dinero que puedes negociar y generalmente se expresa con un formato X:1.

 Por ejemplo, en un modo de juego de apalancamiento 100x, si Bitcoin se mueve 1% en la dirección que indicaste, entonces duplicas tu inversión inicial. Por el contrario, si se mueve 1% en contra de tu posición, perderás todo tu dinero. ¡Cuanto mayor sea el apalancamiento, más fácil será ganar o perder tu dinero!"

playstore_details.title: Crypto & Bitcoin & DeFi Trading Game
playstore_details.description:
Are you interested in cryptocurrencies and Bitcoin trading or even DeFi (Decentralized Finance)? You’re in the right place! Master crypto trading with Altcoin Fantasy’s fun trading simulator games without risking real money.

Why join?
👶 Risk-free bitcoin trading for beginners
✅ Easily learn cryptocurrency trading
💰 Trade Bitcoin and 3000+ altcoins and DeFi tokens
💎 Win trading competitions
⚔️ Compete with traders all over the world.
🤝 Trusted by over 200,000+ traders in 195 countries in all platforms (web and mobile)
🙅‍♂️ It’s FREE. No deposits. No investment required. No purchases necessary.
🎮 25+ different fun games
📈 Exciting margin trading contests with up to 1000x leverage
🤼 Fast 1 vs 1 (PvP) crypto trading contests
🎁 Daily ACF/KIN Points for trading battles

By competing in our trading games, you can experiment with different trading strategies without risking your hard-earned money. Since cryptocurrency prices are pretty volatile, with virtual money, Altcoin Fantasy takes the risky part out of trading and leaves only the fun part while you’re learning.

About Altcoin Fantasy

Altcoin Fantasy helps you try crypto and Bitcoin trading without the risks. Apart from trading, we provide cryptocurrency courses to further sharpen your skills. Choose from cryptos and DeFi tokens, then see what works best and learn about them.

How does Altcoin Fantasy work?

Our cryptocurrency trading simulator uses real order books from cryptocurrency exchanges and you can choose from 1000+ altcoins to trade across all our trading games. We host weekly trading competitions with thousands of players participating. We also host daily trading contests with 25+ different contest types so you will always find the most fun way to learn crypto trading. 

In our trading simulator, all players start with a fantasy portfolio and can start trading cryptocurrencies using their virtual portfolio.

Even if you lose your virtual money, you can simply start over and do better next time!

It’s incredibly easy to start:
Join our crypto trading contests
Make trades, gain experience
Use our courses to sharpen your skills
Level up and win contests

To help you learn crypto trading faster we offer descriptions, real-time charts, cryptocurrency courses, news, crypto alerts. We have guides for beginners at our Altcoin Fantasy Academy to take your trading skills to the next level. 

Our goal is to introduce crypto trading for beginners. Get on top of the DeFi pulse with our game.

What's the catch?
